author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at an upcoming title known as "Better Than Dead", a game that takes the bodycam style and puts you in the shoes of someone who's seen the worst of humanity. This game might be one of the most disturbing titles I've played and I can't wait for it to fully release. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: Human Trafficking Simulator... (Better Than Dead)
